metadata.name: Holographic 1/1
metadata.description:
The missing instruction manual for the self-guided unfolds across marks mapped and uncharted. A jetset look for the modern nomad moving between concrete canopies, facing shorter days and longer shadows. Silver earrings stir kaleidoscopic color, blends of subtle stones, rhinestones, metal undertones. Bold bomber jacket, sleeves patchworked with distinct textiles. 

Synth Graph: a close up center front view 21st century photograph of a beautiful female wearing high fashion streetwear, a red patchwork bomber jacket, blue crystal earrings and a nose piercing, with the busy streets of new york behind her, highly detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
